| 19 | Report path non-obvious | **FIXED** ✓ | Full paths printed at end |
| 20 | No markdown report | **FIXED** ✓ | Markdown report generated alongside JSON |
| 21 | No console summary table | **FIXED** ✓ | Nice box-drawing table with findings |
| 22 | "(polluter unknown)" in constraints | **FIXED** ✓ | Empty constraints when polluter unknown |
| 23 | Different classifications per algorithm | **IMPROVED** | Classification consistent (BRITTLE) but polluter differs |
| 24 | No incremental detection | **OPEN** | Still re-runs fully each time |
