|---|----------|-------|
| 26 | Medium | Console summary shows "VictimTest needs VictimTest" (self-ref) when polluter unknown |
| 27 | Low | `failOnDetection` default changed to `true` — may surprise first-time users |
| 28 | Medium | Multi-module: inter-dependent modules need `mvn install -DskipTests` first (no guidance) |
